            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Student Engagement States Over Time</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='10'>Proportion of students classified as Calm, Moderate, or Tense at each 30-second interval.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
        <view>
          <datasources>
            <datasource caption='eeg_timeseries_final_03' name='federated.0pgr3rq1bap3e11eypihr0gl06aa' />
